  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba - \u0dc0\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0db1\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0db6\u0dc5\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Airman killed in train-van accident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Kalutara North Police, an air force soldier was killed and another soldier was injured in an accident in Kalutara North today (31) when a train and an air force van collided.",
        "The police said that a soldier resident of Wellawaya area who was on duty at Weerawila Air Force Base died in the accident and a soldier resident of Buttala area was injured.",
        "At around 1.33 am, the train was moving towards Colombo from Kalutara, and the police say that the accident occurred when the van was being directed from the beach towards Gallupara through the railway crossing.",
        "The two injured soldiers were admitted to the Kalutara Teaching Hospital, where one soldier died, the police said."
      ],
